Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.19,0:01:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是之前在日向家里露营时发生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.70,0:01:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从富士山那里看肯定更漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.04,0:01:54.26,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(530,416)}去看看富士山吧!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.39,0:02:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.26,0:02:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是枫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.14,0:02:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 心夏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事想跟你商量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 谢谢你们今天能来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这几个人还称不上各位呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想商量什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.58,0:02:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵对富士山有兴趣？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想给小葵一个惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假装是在爬没什么特色的山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然间 让她看到富士山 大吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小枫 你知道什么好地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:51.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用指南书来找找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地域 难易度 做了很多分类呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了小葵我可要加油呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.99,0:03:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离富士山近的是丹泽 南阿尔卑斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这张照片真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北岳？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有好多花田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒 花田 真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.47,0:03:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷鸟 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多么美妙 北岳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏 你找到好地方了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.73,0:03:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北岳 真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}北岳标准高度3143米
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本第二高峰 比富士山更难 面向高手的山
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在去还不行呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少选个面向中级者的山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有其他合适的山呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能看见富士山的山对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 每个都差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多的山太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本的山仅仅是在富士山附近的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹泽山系 秩父山地 八岳 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,围着它的山多着去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真难选
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就选打开的下一页上面的山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也太随便了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候就要一鼓作气呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三增峠？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三增峠山 标准高度1786米
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在富士山附近 登山途中南侧可以眺望富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西侧可以眺望南阿尔卑斯山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山顶的正下面有一个叫做「屏风岩」的绝壁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是著名的攀岩圣地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既可以看见富士山 又没有那么远
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正合适啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么给小葵惊喜的山就决定是三增峠山了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那天之前青不要告诉小葵要去哪里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:14.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是第一次爬三增峠 很是期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去告诉小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒 从饭能也能看到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:42.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向打过来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 从饭能能看到富士…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次爬的山已经决定下来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真突然 是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:05:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地点先保密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:05:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保密…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周六早上六点在东饭能车站集合哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是饭能 是东饭能哦 拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周…她打算带我去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 我还有点小期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毛巾 换洗衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道是什么样的山
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行李这些就够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从三增峠站 顺着登山道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望我们能清楚的看到富士山 愿明天天晴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:52.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:06:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是要保密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先去八王子 在那里换乘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说要去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再去大月
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去哪里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说要保密了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里走要30分钟左右
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微睡一会也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是睡着更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:44.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}葭池温泉前 下吉田 月江寺 富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明白白地说了富士山呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还能清清楚楚的看到富士山呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三增峠山呢 从终点河口湖下车
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在咔嚓咔嚓山坐缆车登山虽然很轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是从一开始就能看见富士山了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以虽然有点累
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要从三增峠站那里爬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得越是累 看到富士山的时候感动就越大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说从路上的屏风岩看富士山非常美呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里给葵一个大惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三增峠站？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里到登山道要30分钟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么必要瞒着我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}觉得好可怕 好可怕啊 往后一看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:08:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:01.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,UFO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是我看错了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏 good job
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前途多舛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像从刚才开始一直都是很普通的路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太像是山路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为一进山路马上就是山顶了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为山顶是那个吧 那个像触角一样的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:36.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 说是三增峠登山道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写了南无阿弥陀佛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在祈愿登山平安呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:57.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山…读什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:09:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山祗神社
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:05.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿我们能够平安归来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:20.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是公共厕所啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是瀑布呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这叫做神铃瀑布
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}日语中神铃和心灵读法一样 心灵有灵魂之意 泛指由灵魂引起的超常现象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是妖怪 是写作神之铃的神铃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就变成很像登山的路了
